2026-01-13  Arnaud VERHILLE
	* Version 1.0
	* Added Lyapunov fractal (type 17) with specialized rendering algorithm
	* Expanded color palettes to 5 smooth variants (SmoothFire, SmoothOcean, SmoothForest, SmoothViolet, SmoothRainbow)
	* Improved fractal rendering system with automatic detection of specialized fractals
	* Updated GUI to support 17 fractal types
	* Enhanced documentation (CLAUDE.md, README.md)
	* Added .gitignore for build artifacts and generated files
	* Improved code organization and maintainability

